{
  "number": 80,
  "name": "سُورَةُ عَبَسَ",
  "englishName": "Abasa",
  "ayahs": [
    {
      "number": 1,
      "text": "He frowned and turned away",
      "juz": 30,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 585,
      "ruku": 522,
      "hizbQuarter": 234,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 2,
      "text": "Because the blind man came unto him.",
      "juz": 30,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 585,
      "ruku": 522,
      "hizbQuarter": 234,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 3,
      "text": "What could inform thee but that he might grow (in grace)",
      "juz": 30,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 585,
      "ruku": 522,
      "hizbQuarter": 234,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 4,
      "text": "Or take heed and so the reminder might avail him?",
      "juz": 30,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 585,
      "ruku": 522,
      "hizbQuarter": 234,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 5,
      "text": "As for him who thinketh himself independent,",
      "juz": 30,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 585,
      "ruku": 522,
      "hizbQuarter": 234,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 6,
      "text": "Unto him thou payest regard.",
      "juz": 30,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 585,
      "ruku": 522,
      "hizbQuarter": 234,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 7,
      "text": "Yet it is not thy concern if he grow not (in grace).",
      "juz": 30,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 585,
      "ruku": 522,
      "hizbQuarter": 234,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 8,
      "text": "But as for him who cometh unto thee with earnest purpose",
      "juz": 30,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 585,
      "ruku": 522,
      "hizbQuarter": 234,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 9,
      "text": "And hath fear,",
      "juz": 30,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 585,
      "ruku": 522,
      "hizbQuarter": 234,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 10,
      "text": "From him thou art distracted.",
      "juz": 30,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 585,
      "ruku": 522,
      "hizbQuarter": 234,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 11,
      "text": "Nay, but verily it is an Admonishment,",
      "juz": 30,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 585,
      "ruku": 522,
      "hizbQuarter": 234,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 12,
      "text": "So let whosoever will pay heed to it,",
      "juz": 30,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 585,
      "ruku": 522,
      "hizbQuarter": 234,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 13,
      "text": "On honoured leaves",
      "juz": 30,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 585,
      "ruku": 522,
      "hizbQuarter": 234,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 14,
      "text": "Exalted, purified,",
      "juz": 30,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 585,
      "ruku": 522,
      "hizbQuarter": 234,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 15,
      "text": "(Set down) by scribes",
      "juz": 30,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 585,
      "ruku": 522,
      "hizbQuarter": 234,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 16,
      "text": "Noble and righteous.",
      "juz": 30,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 585,
      "ruku": 522,
      "hizbQuarter": 234,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 17,
      "text": "Man is (self-)destroyed: how ungrateful!",
      "juz": 30,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 585,
      "ruku": 522,
      "hizbQuarter": 234,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 18,
      "text": "From what thing doth He create him?",
      "juz": 30,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 585,
      "ruku": 522,
      "hizbQuarter": 234,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 19,
      "text": "From a drop of seed. He createth him and proportioneth him,",
      "juz": 30,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 585,
      "ruku": 522,
      "hizbQuarter": 234,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 20,
      "text": "Then maketh the way easy for him,",
      "juz": 30,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 585,
      "ruku": 522,
      "hizbQuarter": 234,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 21,
      "text": "Then causeth him to die, and burieth him;",
      "juz": 30,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 585,
      "ruku": 522,
      "hizbQuarter": 234,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 22,
      "text": "Then, when He will, He bringeth him again to life.",
      "juz": 30,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 585,
      "ruku": 522,
      "hizbQuarter": 234,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 23,
      "text": "Nay, but (man) hath not done what He commanded him.",
      "juz": 30,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 585,
      "ruku": 522,
      "hizbQuarter": 234,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 24,
      "text": "Let man consider his food:",
      "juz": 30,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 585,
      "ruku": 522,
      "hizbQuarter": 234,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 25,
      "text": "How We pour water in showers",
      "juz": 30,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 585,
      "ruku": 522,
      "hizbQuarter": 234,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 26,
      "text": "Then split the earth in clefts",
      "juz": 30,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 585,
      "ruku": 522,
      "hizbQuarter": 234,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 27,
      "text": "And cause the grain to grow therein",
      "juz": 30,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 585,
      "ruku": 522,
      "hizbQuarter": 234,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 28,
      "text": "And grapes and green fodder",
      "juz": 30,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 585,
      "ruku": 522,
      "hizbQuarter": 234,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 29,
      "text": "And olive-trees and palm-trees",
      "juz": 30,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 585,
      "ruku": 522,
      "hizbQuarter": 234,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 30,
      "text": "And garden-closes of thick foliage",
      "juz": 30,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 585,
      "ruku": 522,
      "hizbQuarter": 234,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 31,
      "text": "And fruits and grasses:",
      "juz": 30,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 585,
      "ruku": 522,
      "hizbQuarter": 234,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 32,
      "text": "Provision for you and your cattle.",
      "juz": 30,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 585,
      "ruku": 522,
      "hizbQuarter": 234,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 33,
      "text": "But when the Shout cometh",
      "juz": 30,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 585,
      "ruku": 522,
      "hizbQuarter": 234,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 34,
      "text": "On the day when a man fleeth from his brother",
      "juz": 30,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 585,
      "ruku": 522,
      "hizbQuarter": 234,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 35,
      "text": "And his mother and his father",
      "juz": 30,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 585,
      "ruku": 522,
      "hizbQuarter": 234,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 36,
      "text": "And his wife and his children,",
      "juz": 30,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 585,
      "ruku": 522,
      "hizbQuarter": 234,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 37,
      "text": "Every man that day will have concern enough to make him heedless (of others).",
      "juz": 30,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 585,
      "ruku": 522,
      "hizbQuarter": 234,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 38,
      "text": "On that day faces will be bright as dawn,",
      "juz": 30,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 585,
      "ruku": 522,
      "hizbQuarter": 234,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 39,
      "text": "Laughing, rejoicing at good news;",
      "juz": 30,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 585,
      "ruku": 522,
      "hizbQuarter": 234,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 40,
      "text": "And other faces, on that day, with dust upon them,",
      "juz": 30,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 585,
      "ruku": 522,
      "hizbQuarter": 234,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 41,
      "text": "Veiled in darkness,",
      "juz": 30,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 585,
      "ruku": 522,
      "hizbQuarter": 234,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 42,
      "text": "Those are the disbelievers, the wicked.",
      "juz": 30,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 585,
      "ruku": 522,
      "hizbQuarter": 234,
      "sajda": false
    }
  ]
}